---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Blog header section -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--base02) 0%, var(--base03) 100%); padding: 3rem 1rem; text-align: center; color: var(--base2);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--base2);">Security Insights Blog</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;">
        Expert analysis, best practices, and insights on modern cybersecurity challenges and solutions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main style="max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem;">
      <!-- Featured post -->
      <div style="background: rgba(7,54,66,0.07); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);">
        <span style="text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;">Featured Post</span>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--fg);">
          <a href="/blog/first-post/" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">
            Zero Trust Architecture: Beyond the Perimeter
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--base01); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          Published: <strong>{new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</strong> • 10 min read
        </p>
        <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          As organizations increasingly adopt remote work and cloud services, traditional perimeter-based security models are no longer effective. Learn how Zero Trust Architecture addresses modern security challenges by verifying every access request regardless of source.
        </p>
        <a href="/blog/first-post/" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; display: inline-flex; align-items: center;">
          Read More <span style="margin-left: 5px;">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Recent posts -->
      <div>
        <h3 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; font-size: 1.4rem;">Recent Posts</h3>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
          <div style="background: rgba(7,54,66,0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; transition: transform 0.2s;">
            <span style="color: var(--base01); font-size: 0.9rem;">May 5, 2025</span>
            <h3 style="margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">
              <a href="/blog/another-post/" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">
                Effective Cloud Security Controls
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p style="line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--fg);">Essential security controls for protecting cloud environments while enabling business agility and innovation.</p>
            <a href="/blog/another-post/" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;">Read article →</a>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: rgba(7,54,66,0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; transition: transform 0.2s;">
            <span style="color: var(--base01); font-size: 0.9rem;">April 22, 2025</span>
            <h3 style="margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">
              <a href="#" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">
                Incident Response in Modern Enterprises
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p style="line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--fg);">Building effective incident response plans that minimize impact and ensure business continuity.</p>
            <a href="#" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;">Read article →</a>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: rgba(7,54,66,0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; transition: transform 0.2s;">
            <span style="color: var(--base01); font-size: 0.9rem;">April 10, 2025</span>
            <h3 style="margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">
              <a href="#" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">
                The Human Element in Cybersecurity
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p style="line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--fg);">How effective security awareness programs can transform employees from vulnerabilities to security assets.</p>
            <a href="#" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;">Read article →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Topics -->
      <div style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; font-size: 1.4rem;">Security Topics</h3>
        
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.8rem;">
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">Zero Trust</a>
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">Cloud Security</a>
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">Incident Response</a>
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">Threat Intelligence</a>
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">Compliance</a>
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">Security Architecture</a>
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">IAM</a>
          <a href="#" style="background: var(--base02); color: var(--base2); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s;">Security Awareness</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
